6
Use the Shortage of Liberties
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b Black to play\b0 .
\par
\par It is a capturing race between Black \'a1\'e3 stones and White \'a1\'e2 stones.
\par
\par Black has two liberties and White has three, so it seems it is hard for Black to win this capturing race. However if he makes use of the shortage of liberties, he can win.
\par }
