Dia. 01 Bad Reading 1
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Some people might though about playing on the outside liberty at 1.
\par If White plays dansu at 2, Black plays a 3 and wins.
\par
\par White can't play from both side because of shortage of liberties. However this sequence is terrible.
\par
\par White could play dansu at 3 instead of 2 and then Black is captured.
\par
\par }
