Dia. 02 Bad Reading 2
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Shall we check Black 1?
\par If White plays dansu at 2, Black captures at 3 and wins the capturing race.
\par
\par It is \cf1\b eye vs. no eye\cf0\b0  situation up to 5.
\par
\par However this is another bad reading. White can play at A instead of 2 and resist with pae.
\par
\par It is a failure, because Black can win without pae.
\par }
