Dia. 03 Bad Reading 3
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par How about the 1-2 vital point in the corner?
\par If Black plays the diagonal move at 1, it looks like he is going to win the capturing race.
\par
\par If White plays at 2, Black fills the liberty with 3 and Black wins. It is \cf1\b eye vs. no eye\cf0\b0  situation.
\par However this is another bad reading.
\par }
