Dia. 04 White's Plan/Pae
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par After Black \'a1\'e3, White has a nice play with 1. It is a bit difficult move.
\par
\par Black has to capture with 2 and then what happens if White plays at 3?
\par Yes, that's right. It is pae.
\par Therefore Black \'a1\'e3 is not the vital point, but a careless move.
\par
\par
\par
\par }
