[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black 1 is the only move we haven't tried yet.
\par Black can win the capturing race with this calm descending move at 1.
\par
\par It makes use of White's shortage of liberties.
\par }
